00:14:58,380 --> 00:14:59,130
ÂĄKin-san!

211
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:13,640
ÂĄEl monstruo vendrĂĄ directo hacia aquĂ­ en cuanto perciba el olor de su crĂ­a!

212
00:15:17,370 --> 00:15:19,150
ÂĄA un lado!

213
00:15:21,610 --> 00:15:22,900
ÂĄViene hacia aquĂ­!

214
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:37,370
ÂżEh?

215
00:15:37,370 --> 00:15:39,170
ÂĄÂżKin-chan ha vuelto a robar?!

216
00:15:39,170 --> 00:15:42,900
ÂĄLo siento, yo se lo pago!

217
00:15:46,220 --> 00:15:48,430
Kin-chan, consigue un empleo.

218
00:15:48,430 --> 00:15:50,390
ÂĄSiempre te estĂĄn persiguiendo los yakuza!

219
00:15:50,390 --> 00:15:52,220
ÂĄUn dĂ­a te matarĂĄn!

220
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:53,220
ÂĄNo importa!

221
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:55,600
ÂĄNadie me llorarĂĄ si muero!

222
00:16:00,160 --> 00:16:03,420
ÂĄDuele, no me golpees con rocas!

223
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:08,500
ÂĄDevuĂŠlveme a Tsuru!

224
00:16:45,820 --> 00:16:47,280
ÂĄDetente, muchacho!

225
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:50,910
ÂĄSi hieres al Dios de la MontaĂąa, 
serĂĄ el fin del PaĂ­s de Wa!

226
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:53,780
ÂĄLe voy a rajar la panza!

227
00:16:53,780 --> 00:16:56,410
ÂĄNo eres ningĂşn dios!

228
00:16:56,410 --> 00:16:59,290
ÂĄDevuĂŠlveme a Tsuru!

229
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:06,710
ÂĄKin-san!

230
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:20,190
ÂĄKin-san, detente!

231
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:23,860
Tiene agallas, Âżeh?

232
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:43,830
ÂĄSi Tsuru muere por mi culpa,

233
00:17:49,210 --> 00:17:52,110
me gustarĂ­a morir a mĂ­ tambiĂŠn!

234
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:23,000
ÂĄÂżEs esto lo que buscas, jabalĂ­?!

235
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,290
ÂĄEse es Kouzuki Oden, el hijo maldito!

236
00:18:25,290 --> 00:18:27,290
ÂĄOtra vez fue ĂŠl!

237
00:18:27,290 --> 00:18:30,460
ÂĄTodo lo ocasionĂł ĂŠl!

238
00:18:30,460 --> 00:18:32,170
ÂżHacemos un estofado de jabalĂ­?

239
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:36,600
ÂĄÂżCĂłmo te atreves a desencadenar
 algo tan terrible?!

240
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:38,220
ÂĄDevuĂŠlveme a mi madre!

241
00:18:39,390 --> 00:18:40,180
Se equivocan.

242
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:42,060
ÂĄSe equivocan!

243
00:18:42,060 --> 00:18:43,730
ÂĄDevuĂŠlveme a mi hija!

244
00:18:43,730 --> 00:18:48,230
ÂĄEl que trajo al jabalĂ­ blanco fui yo!

245
00:18:48,230 --> 00:18:52,650
ÂĄTodos estĂĄn sufriendo por mi culpa!

246
00:19:05,290 --> 00:19:07,390
ÂĄOden Nitouryuu!

247
00:19:41,620 --> 00:19:43,580
ÂĄTougen Shirataki!

248
00:19:41,410 --> 00:19:44,410
Mola

249
00:19:41,410 --> 00:19:44,410
Shi

250
00:19:41,410 --> 00:19:44,410
Chibukai

251
00:19:41,410 --> 00:19:44,410
Fansub!

252
00:19:41,410 --> 00:19:44,410
Cascada blanca paradisĂ­aca.

253
00:19:43,580 --> 00:19:45,080
ÂĄÂżEh?!

254
00:19:43,580 --> 00:19:45,080
ÂĄÂżEh?!

255
00:19:51,290 --> 00:19:53,050
ÂĄEs increĂ­ble!

256
00:19:53,050 --> 00:19:55,010
ÂĄVolvamos a casa!

257
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:05,100
Dicen que con las personas y las casas 
que el jabalĂ­ se tragĂł enteras...

258
00:20:05,100 --> 00:20:10,060
...se podrĂ­a haber fundado una
 nueva ciudad en su estĂłmago.

259
00:20:10,060 --> 00:20:16,650
Una cuarta parte de la ciudad fue destruida, pero, milagrosamente, nadie muriĂł.

260
00:20:16,650 --> 00:20:19,420
ÂĄKin-chan!

261
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:28,370
Oden, eso estuvo genial.

262
00:20:28,370 --> 00:20:31,630
Estuvo tan genial que casi grito.

263
00:20:31,630 --> 00:20:33,080
ÂĄQuiero darle las gracias,

264
00:20:33,080 --> 00:20:34,500
pero no puedo!

265
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:36,330
ÂĄPorque todo esto fue su culpa!

266
00:20:36,330 --> 00:20:37,720
ÂĄEs malvado!

267
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:39,890
ÂĄEscuchen!

268
00:20:39,890 --> 00:20:41,600
Lo que en realidad sucediĂł...

269
00:20:43,930 --> 00:20:46,020
ÂĄNo hagas estupideces!

270
00:20:46,020 --> 00:20:48,520
ÂĄOden-sama!

271
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:53,440
Me parte el corazĂłn entregarle esto 
en un momento de alegrĂ­a...

272
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:55,060
Ya veo.

273
00:20:55,060 --> 00:20:57,150
ÂĄHa cortado toda relaciĂłn conmigo 
y me expulsĂł de la capital!

274
00:20:58,320 --> 00:21:00,860
ÂĄEsto es ridĂ­culo, shogun-dono!

275
00:21:00,860 --> 00:21:07,370
ÂĄSignifica que ni usted ni la Capital 
de las Flores pueden conmigo!

276
00:21:07,370 --> 00:21:08,960
ÂĄAcepto el rompimiento!

277
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:11,080
ÂĄMe irĂŠ a otro lado!

278
00:21:11,080 --> 00:21:13,290
ÂĄCuando se oculte el sol, dormirĂŠ 
en donde sea que me encuentre!

279
00:21:13,290 --> 00:21:16,650
ÂĄAh, cuĂĄnta hambre tengo!

280
00:21:16,650 --> 00:21:22,800
El incidente del Dios de la MontaĂąa en el 
PaĂ­s de Wa sucediĂł cuando Oden aĂşn era joven.

281
00:21:24,470 --> 00:21:26,470
ÂżEstĂĄs llorando, Kin-chan?

282
00:21:26,470 --> 00:21:27,890
ÂĄClaro que no!

283
00:21:27,890 --> 00:21:32,020
ÂĄOtsuru, darĂ­a mi vida por ĂŠl!

284
00:21:32,020 --> 00:21:33,060
ÂĄEstĂĄs llorando!

285
00:21:33,060 --> 00:21:34,110
ÂĄYo tambiĂŠn...

286
00:21:34,110 --> 00:21:35,900
...darĂ­a mi vida por ĂŠl!

287
00:21:35,900 --> 00:21:38,190
ÂĄOye, espera, Denjiro!

288
00:21:38,190 --> 00:21:39,440
ÂĄOh, Kin-chan!

289
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:42,700
ÂĄKouzuki Oden, Kouzuki Oden, Kouzuki Oden!

290
00:21:42,700 --> 00:21:44,320
ÂĄEs increĂ­ble!

291
00:21:44,320 --> 00:21:45,580
ÂĄLo he decidido!

292
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:47,790
ÂĄLo seguirĂŠ toda la vida!

293
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:50,790
ÂĄYo lo admirĂŠ primero!

294
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:52,080
ÂĄPero no tan intensamente!

295
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:54,270
ÂĄYo soy su primer seguidor!

296
00:21:54,270 --> 00:21:57,210
ÂĄDesearĂ­a ser libre como ellos!

297
00:21:57,210 --> 00:22:04,460
Se dice que los hombres presentes realizaron tal esfuerzo para resistir las ganas de seguir a Oden...

298
00:22:04,460 --> 00:22:07,630
...que incluso la capital pudo haberse inclinado.

299
00:22:11,180 --> 00:22:12,810
ÂĄPase, pase, Oden-sama!

300
00:22:12,810 --> 00:22:14,350
ÂĄEs un honor!

301
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:17,690
ÂĄYasuie-sama lo ha estado esperando!

302
00:22:17,690 --> 00:22:20,070
ÂĄNo mientas, eso no es cierto!

303
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:23,110
SĂ­, Âżpor quĂŠ habrĂ­a de esperar...

304
00:22:23,110 --> 00:22:25,530
...a un idiota que ha sido 
expulsado de la capital?

305
00:22:25,530 --> 00:22:27,400
ÂĄÂżQuĂŠ quieres, Oden?!

306
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:29,240
ÂżTe sientes tan importante 
para traer seguidores?

307
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:30,580
ÂĄHola, tĂ­o!

308
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:32,460
ÂĄNo me llames asĂ­!

309
00:22:33,710 --> 00:22:34,950
ÂĄAh, un momento!

310
00:22:34,950 --> 00:22:35,960
ÂĄHay un charco!

311
00:22:38,130 --> 00:22:43,970
ÂĄAdelante, pĂ­senme y crucen a salvo!

312
00:22:43,970 --> 00:22:46,550
ÂĄEste me da escalofrĂ­os!

313
00:22:46,550 --> 00:22:49,350
Es mi nuevo sirviente.

314
00:22:49,350 --> 00:22:50,640
ÂĄSĂ­, sĂ­!

315
00:22:50,640 --> 00:22:53,230
ÂĄYasuie-sama me acogiĂł!

316
00:22:54,230 --> 00:22:57,690
Soy Orochi, su sirviente.

